originContent: **[Apache RocketMQ](https://rocketmq.apache.org) is a distributed messaging and streaming platform with low latency, high performance and reliability, trillion-level capacity and flexible scalability.**
translatedContent: **[Apache RocketMQ](https://rocketmq.apache.org) es una plataforma distribuida de mensajería y streaming con baja latencia, alto rendimiento y fiabilidad, capacidad a nivel de billones y escalabilidad flexible.**

originContent: It offers a variety of features:
* Messaging patterns including publish/subscribe, request/reply and streaming
translatedContent: * Patrones de mensajería que incluyen publicar/suscribir, solicitud/respuesta y streaming

originContent: * Built-in fault tolerance and high availability configuration options base on [DLedger Controller](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apache/rocketmq/develop/docs/en/controller/quick_start.md)
translatedContent: * Opciones integradas de tolerancia a fallos y alta disponibilidad basadas en [DLedger Controller](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apache/rocketmq/develop/docs/en/controller/quick_start.md)

originContent: * Built-in message tracing capability, also support opentracing
translatedContent: * Capacidad integrada de rastreo de mensajes, también soporta opentracing

originContent: * Versatile big-data and streaming ecosystem integration
translatedContent: * Integración versátil con ecosistemas de big data y streaming

originContent: * Message retroactivity by time or offset
translatedContent: * Retroactividad de mensajes por tiempo o desplazamiento

originContent: * Reliable FIFO and strict ordered messaging in the same queue
translatedContent: * Mensajería FIFO confiable y orden estricta en la misma cola

originContent: * Efficient pull and push consumption model
translatedContent: * Modelo eficiente de consumo pull y push

originContent: * Million-level message accumulation capacity in a single queue
translatedContent: * Capacidad de acumulación de mensajes a nivel de millones en una sola cola

originContent: * Multiple messaging protocols like gRPC, MQTT, JMS and OpenMessaging
translatedContent: * Múltiples protocolos de mensajería como gRPC, MQTT, JMS y OpenMessaging
* Arquitectura flexible de despliegue distribuido y escalable
* Sistema de intercambio de mensajes por lotes ultrarrápido

originContent: * Various message filter mechanics such as SQL and Tag
translatedContent: * Diversos mecanismos de filtrado de mensajes como SQL y Tag

originContent: * Docker images for isolated testing and cloud isolated clusters
translatedContent: * Imágenes Docker para pruebas aisladas y clústeres aislados en la nube

originContent: * Feature-rich administrative dashboard for configuration, metrics and monitoring
translatedContent: * Panel administrativo completo para configuración, métricas y monitoreo

originContent: * Free open source connectors, for both sources and sinks
translatedContent: * Conectores libres y de código abierto, tanto para fuentes como para destinos

originContent: This paragraph guides you through steps of installing RocketMQ in different ways.
translatedContent: Este párrafo te guía a través de los pasos para instalar RocketMQ de diferentes maneras.

originContent: For local development and testing, only one instance will be created for each component.
translatedContent: Para el desarrollo y pruebas locales, solo se creará una instancia para cada componente.

originContent: RocketMQ runs on all major operating systems and requires only a Java JDK version 8 or higher to be installed.
translatedContent: RocketMQ funciona en todos los principales sistemas operativos y solo requiere que se instale una versión de Java JDK 8 o superior.

originContent: For Windows users, click [here](https://dist.apache.org/repos/dist/release/rocketmq/5.3.3/rocketmq-all-5.3.3-bin-release.zip) to download the 5.3.3 RocketMQ binary release,

originContent: unpack it to your local disk, such as `D:\rocketmq`.
translatedContent: descomprímala en su disco local, por ejemplo en `D:\rocketmq`.

originContent: You can run RocketMQ on your own machine within Docker containers,
translatedContent: Puedes ejecutar RocketMQ en tu propia máquina dentro de contenedores Docker,

originContent: `host` network will be used to expose listening port in the container.
translatedContent: se utilizará la red `host` para exponer el puerto de escucha en el contenedor.

originContent: You can also run a RocketMQ cluster within a Kubernetes cluster using [RocketMQ Operator](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-operator).
translatedContent: También puedes ejecutar un clúster de RocketMQ dentro de un clúster de Kubernetes usando [RocketMQ Operator](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-operator).

originContent: Before your operations, make sure that `kubectl` and related kubeconfig file installed on your machine.
translatedContent: Antes de tus operaciones, asegúrate de que `kubectl` y el archivo kubeconfig relacionado estén instalados en tu máquina.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Streams](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-streams): A lightweight stream computing engine based on Apache RocketMQ.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Streams](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-streams): Un motor de computación en flujo ligero basado en Apache RocketMQ.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Flink](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-flink): The Apache RocketMQ connector of Apache Flink that supports source and sink connector in data stream and Table.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Flink](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-flink): El conector de Apache RocketMQ para Apache Flink que soporta conectores fuente y sumidero en flujo de datos y Tabla.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Spring](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-spring): A project which helps developers quickly integrate Apache RocketMQ with Spring Boot.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Spring](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-spring): Un proyecto que ayuda a los desarrolladores a integrar rápidamente Apache RocketMQ con Spring Boot.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Exporter](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-exporter): An Apache RocketMQ exporter for Prometheus.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Exporter](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-exporter): Un exportador de Apache RocketMQ para Prometheus.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Operator](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-operator): Providing a way to run an Apache RocketMQ cluster on Kubernetes.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Operator](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-operator): Proporciona una forma de ejecutar un clúster de Apache RocketMQ en Kubernetes.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Docker](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-docker): The Git repo of the Docker Image for Apache RocketMQ.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Docker](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-docker): El repositorio Git de la imagen Docker para Apache RocketMQ.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Dashboard](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-dashboard): Operation and maintenance console of Apache RocketMQ.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Dashboard](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-dashboard): Consola de operación y mantenimiento de Apache RocketMQ.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Connect](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-connect): A tool for scalably and reliably streaming data between Apache RocketMQ and other systems.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ Connect](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-connect): Una herramienta para transmitir datos de forma escalable y confiable entre Apache RocketMQ y otros sistemas.

originContent: * [RocketMQ MQTT](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-mqtt): A new MQTT protocol architecture model, based on which Apache RocketMQ can better support messages from terminals such as IoT devices and Mobile APP.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ MQTT](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-mqtt): Un nuevo modelo de arquitectura de protocolo MQTT, sobre el cual Apache RocketMQ puede soportar mejor mensajes de terminales como dispositivos IoT y aplicaciones móviles.

originContent: * [RocketMQ EventBridge](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-eventbridge): EventBridge make it easier to build a event-driven application.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ EventBridge](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-eventbridge): EventBridge facilita la construcción de una aplicación orientada a eventos.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Incubating Community Projects](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals): Incubator community projects of Apache RocketMQ, including [logappender](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/logappender), [rocketmq-ansible](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/rocketmq-ansible), [rocketmq-beats-integration](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/rocketmq-beats-integration), [rocketmq-cloudevents-binding](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/rocketmq-cloudevents-binding), etc.
translatedContent: * [Proyectos de la Comunidad en Incubación de RocketMQ](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals): Proyectos comunitarios incubados de Apache RocketMQ, incluyendo [logappender](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/logappender), [rocketmq-ansible](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/rocketmq-ansible), [rocketmq-beats-integration](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/rocketmq-beats-integration), [rocketmq-cloudevents-binding](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-externals/tree/master/rocketmq-cloudevents-binding), etc.

originContent: * [RocketMQ Site](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-site): The repository for Apache RocketMQ website.
translatedContent: * [Sitio RocketMQ](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-site): El repositorio para el sitio web de Apache RocketMQ.

originContent: * [RocketMQ E2E](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-e2e): A project for testing Apache RocketMQ, including end-to-end, performance, compatibility tests.
translatedContent: * [RocketMQ E2E](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq-e2e): Un proyecto para probar Apache RocketMQ, incluyendo pruebas de extremo a extremo, rendimiento y compatibilidad.

originContent: We always welcome new contributions, whether for trivial cleanups, [big new features](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq/wiki/RocketMQ-Improvement-Proposal) or other material rewards, more details see [here](http://rocketmq.apache.org/docs/how-to-contribute/).
translatedContent: Siempre damos la bienvenida a nuevas contribuciones, ya sea para limpiezas triviales, [grandes nuevas funcionalidades](https://github.com/apache/rocketmq/wiki/RocketMQ-Improvement-Proposal) u otras recompensas materiales, más detalles véase [aquí](http://rocketmq.apache.org/docs/how-to-contribute/).
